# Shannon
RNA-Seq


1. Installation:  
  1.1 Metis install
      See here for instructions on installing metis: http://glaros.dtc.umn.edu/gkhome/metis/metis/download
  1.2 CVXOPT install
      See here for installing 
      pip install cvxopt
  1.3 Jellyfish install
  1.4 Quorum install (optional but recommended)
      

2. Running
  2.1 Navigate to the Shannon directory
  2.2 Run the folllowing command
        python shannon.py working_directory_for_shannon read_file   for single end reads  (the reads should be in format 
        python shannon.py working_directory_for_shannon read_pair_1 read_pair_2   for single end reads

